query: SELECT m.id, m.title, m.author, me.id as eval_id, me.overallScore, me.verdict, me.generatedAt FROM manuals m LEFT JOIN manual_evaluations me ON m.id = me.manualId WHERE m.title LIKE '%Principi di Chimica%' AND m.author LIKE '%Atkins%' LIMIT 1;
